test_name: FTDBIST should be present if all subquestions are present
short_desc: If al of (FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR) are not blank, then FTDBIST must equal their sum
full_desc: If all of (FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR) are not blank, then Q8. FTDBIST(BIS Total Score) must equal the sum of Q1. FTDWORKU, Q2. FTDMIST, Q3. FTDCRIT, Q4. FTDWORR, Q5. FTDBAD, Q6. FTDPOOR, Q7. FTDFFEAR
test_logic: If all of (FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR) are not blank and FTDBIST ne sum of FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR
comp_vars: FTDBIST, FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR

test_name: FTDBIST should be missing if any subquestions are missing
short_desc: If any of (FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR) are missing, FTDBIST must = 88
full_desc: If any of (FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR) are blank, then Q8. FTDBIST(BIS Total Score) must = 88
test_logic: If any of (FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR) are blank and FTDBIST ne 88
comp_vars: FTDBIST, FTDWORKU, FTDMIST, FTDCRIT, FTDWORR, FTDBAD, FTDPOOR, FTDFFEAR

short_desc: FRMDATEC4F must not be from date before form was released
full_desc: Q0a. FRMDATEC4F (C4F form date) must not be from date before form was released (2012)
